                      -1 = Libs: / -2 = Devs: / -3 = Sys:Classes/Datatypes


@{B}V 0.9  / 04.03.1999@{UB} - Last beta-release.

                      Version for 'CheckGuide' to test it.


@{B}V 0.4  / 03.03.1999@{UB} - Recompiled (internal)

                    - Preversion vbcc 0.7 changed about releaseversion 0.7

                      recompiling of all lib's, library's and programs

                      with new, actual includes and libs from vbcc.

                    - Many tests.


@{B}V 0.3  / 28.02.1999@{UB} - Preversion (internal).

                    - Build-in language now english.

                    - Texts moved to files.


@{B}V 0.2  / 27.02.1999@{UB} - Beta-version (internal).

                    - Bugs in recursion ExAll() fixed (used many stack).

                    - Outputfiles (ram:) for check.

                    - Output centralized and optimized.

                    - CPU-check changed.

                    - Bug (GURU) in split versionstring fixed.

                    - Internal flag (-v) included (verbose info's).
 

@{B}V 0.1  / 23.02.1999@{UB} - First version (internal).
